		<p>During the last ten years, the university has advanced greatly in promoting international mobility. Programmes and many others support this process. With the help of the this programmes, University has hosted four long-term professors, two Mobilitas researchers and five postdocs as well as four ERMOS postdocs from different countries.</p> 	</div>

	
